text: Maxence Medjelled (born 4 November 1994) is a French professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for AC Arles-Avignon. ==Club career== Medjelled made his full professional debut in a 2–2 Ligue 2 draw against Tours in May 2014, coming on the pitch as a substitute for Adrien Coulomb. ==References== ==External links== * * * Maxence Medjelled foot-national.com Profile Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Association football midfielders Category:French footballers Category:Ligue 2 players Category:AC Arles-Avignon players
